<font color="#FFFFFF" face="Arial">
<strong>Band of Rodcet Nife - AC 0</strong>
<font size=-1></font><BR>
Slot: <a href="/armour/fingers.shtml">Fingers</a><BR>
Weight: 0.1 - All Races<BR>
Classes: <a href="/bard/armour/fingers.shtml">BRD</a>, <a href="/cleric/armour/fingers.shtml">CLR</a>, <a href="/druid/armour/fingers.shtml">DRU</a>, <a href="/enchanter/armour/fingers.shtml">ENC</a>, <a href="/magician/armour/fingers.shtml">MAG</a>, <a href="/monk/armour/fingers.shtml">MNK</a>, <a href="/paladin/armour/fingers.shtml">PAL</a>, <a href="/ranger/armour/fingers.shtml">RNG</a>, <a href="/rogue/armour/fingers.shtml">ROG</a>, <a href="/warrior/armour/fingers.shtml">WAR</a>, <a href="/wizard/armour/fingers.shtml">WIZ</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(No Drop) (Lore) <BR>
(INT +3) (Mana +10) </font>
<BR>
Submitted By: TregareUS<BR>

