<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I found that a good way to increase Temple of Life faction was by giving Chesgard in the House of Thunder bandit sashes from the bandits in West Karana.  The usual reward for a shash is a bronze weapon, which is not bad in itself.  18 sashes took me from dubious to amiable with the Temple of Life.</font></td></tr></table>
